<DOCNO> FBIS3-48858 </DOCNO>
<HT>    "dreas020_c_94020" </HT>


<HEADER>
<AU>   FBIS-EAS-94-020 </AU>
Document Type:Daily Report 
<DATE1>  31 Jan 1994 </DATE1>

