<F P=100> North Korea </F>
<H3> <TI>   Works of Kim Il-song, Kim Chong-il on Display </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  SK3101113694 Pyongyang KCNA in English 1044 GMT 31 Jan 94 </F>
<F P=103> SK3101113694 </F>
<F P=104>  Pyongyang KCNA </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Pyongyang, January 31 (KCNA) -- Works of the great 
leader President Kim Il-song and the dear leader Comrade Kim 
Chong- il which had been translated and published in more than 
20 countries were recently displayed at the exhibition of the 
works of Comrade Kim Il-song in the People's Palace of Culture, 
Pyongyang. 
  On display at the exhibition are now works of more than 400 
kinds which were brought out in over 50 national languages in 
nearly 100 countries in all. 
  The newly displayed works were translated into more than ten 
languages including Dutch, Bengalee, Urdu, Hindi, Persian and 
Polish. 
  Among them are the famous works of President Kim Il-song 
"Young People Must Accomplish the Revolutionary Cause of Chuche, 
Upholding the Leadership of the Party," "10-Point Programme of 
the Great Unity of the Whole Nation for the Reunification of the 
Country" and "Enhancing the Role of the Popular Masses Is the 
Guarantee for Victory in the Cause of Independence" and others. 
  And the works of Comrade Kim Chong-il "The Workers' Party of 
Korea Organizes and Guides all the Victories of Our People," 
"The Historical Lesson in Building Socialism and the General 
Line of Our Party" and "Abuses of Socialism Are Intolerable" are 
also included. 
  The works give perfect answers to the theoretical and 
practical questions arising in the revolution and construction 
at present. 

</TEXT>

