<F P=100> SLOVENIA </F>
<H3> <TI>   FRY Visas Only To Be Issued at Consulates </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  AU3012193893 Ljubljana Radio Slovenia Network in Slovene 
1430 GMT 30 Dec 93 </F>

<F P=103> AU3012193893 </F>
<F P=104>  Ljubljana Radio Slovenia Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Slovene </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] The Slovene Foreign Ministry has announced that 
from the beginning of 1994 citizens of the so-called FRY will 
have to obtain an entry or a transit visa from the closest 
diplomatic or consular mission of the Republic of Slovenia 
abroad prior to entering our country. The conditions for issue 
of visas remain unchanged, but as of tomorrow the Slovene border 
authorities on international border crossings will no longer 
issue visas to the Yugoslav citizens. 

</TEXT>

