<H3> <TI>   Troops Reinforce Border With Serbia </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD3112104093 Budapest Kossuth Radio Network in Hungarian 
1000 GMT 31 Dec 93 </F>

<F P=103> LD3112104093 </F>
<F P=104>  Budapest Kossuth Radio Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Hungarian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Border Guards have reinforced the protection of the 
Hungarian-Serbian border. They fear that due to the 
introduction of a travel tax in rump Yugoslavia that is to come 
into force soon, many people will try to come across to Hungary 
illegally. Border Guard Spikesman Attila Krisan said that as a 
result of the new decree, which is valid as of midnight, the 
